    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "\nThe main motivation is to provide topics more freedom to grow.  Many wiki topics have grown beyond the comfortable boundaries of a single wiki page. Keeping summaries and discussions together creates huge pages, and leads to tension between [[Thread Mode]] and [[Document Mode]]. Refactoring into completely separate pages often seems to harm the coherence of the ideas. I hope that subpages will allow more thorough discussion and exploration of ideas, while making it easier for people to find or avoid topics depending on their interests.",
      "id": "c4a9f13e0e5e11ce81a4b68423c51d05"
